(1, 20, 'I am a highly skilled freelancer with expertise in computer programming, software development, and system architecture. Proficient in multiple programming languages, I excel in creating efficient and scalable solutions for various projects. My skills extend to audiovisual production, where I bring creativity to life through video editing, animation, and multimedia creation. Additionally, I possess a deep understanding of 3D design and animation, producing captivating visuals for diverse applications. In the realm of marketing and communication, I leverage my technical background to develop innovative strategies, ensuring effective communication and promotion of products or services.', 'I am currently working on a dynamic software project that involves creating a user-friendly interface and implementing advanced functionalities. This project encompasses elements of audiovisual content, incorporating engaging multimedia to enhance user experience. The 3D and animation aspects bring a unique flair to the project, setting it apart in terms of visual appeal. The marketing and communication strategy involves positioning the product for optimal market reach, utilizing targeted campaigns and effective messaging. This comprehensive project showcases my diverse skill set, bringing together technology, creativity, and strategic thinking to deliver a top-tier solution.'),
(2, 45, 'As a freelancer, my skills span across the fields of IT, audiovisual production, 3D modeling, and marketing. With a strong foundation in software development, I specialize in creating robust applications tailored to client needs. In the audiovisual realm, I excel in video production, editing, and animation, bringing visual stories to life. My proficiency in 3D design allows me to create immersive and realistic environments. In marketing and communication, I leverage my technical expertise to develop effective campaigns that resonate with the target audience.', 'I am currently working on a multimedia project that integrates cutting-edge technology with artistic expression. This project involves developing a custom software solution, incorporating visually stunning 3D animations and captivating audiovisual content. The marketing strategy focuses on creating a buzz around the project, utilizing social media and targeted advertising. This multifaceted project not only demonstrates my technical prowess but also showcases my ability to deliver compelling and marketable products.'),
(3, 30, 'I bring a diverse set of skills to the freelance world, covering IT, audiovisual production, 3D animation, and marketing. My expertise lies in developing scalable and efficient software solutions, addressing complex challenges in the IT domain. In audiovisual production, I specialize in creating visually appealing content through video editing, animation, and multimedia production. The 3D and animation skills add a creative edge to my repertoire. In marketing and communication, I excel in crafting strategic plans to elevate brand visibility and engagement.', 'Currently, I am involved in a project that combines technology and creativity. This project entails developing a software solution with a focus on user experience, incorporating 3D elements and engaging audiovisual content. The marketing aspect involves creating a cohesive brand image and executing targeted communication strategies. This project reflects my ability to seamlessly integrate technology and creativity to deliver impactful solutions.'),
(4, 10, 'Development of Custom Games.\nCreation of bespoke video games using languages such as Unity and C#, with expertise in mobile and web-based game development.\n\nConception de Jeux et Game Design.\nExpertise in game design, including user experience (UX) design, game mechanics and storytelling, for compelling game experiences.\n\nMulti-platform development.\nAdapting games for different platforms such as PC, consoles, and mobile, to maximise reach and accessibility.\n\nMaintenance et Mises à Jour.\nWe offer ongoing maintenance and update services to guarantee the durability and quality of the games we develop.\n\nWeb Development and Cloud Services Integration.\nCompétence dans le développement web et l''intégration de services cloud pour des fonctionnalités en ligne dans les jeux.', 'Virtual Life Simulation.\nTo develop a realistic life simulation game, offering players the chance to create and manage avatars in a virtual environment, simulating various aspects of everyday life.\n\nVirtual Reality (VR) Educational Game.\nTo create an educational virtual reality game focusing on interactive learning. This project could explore subjects such as history, science or foreign languages in an immersive way.\n\nMulti-platform strategy.\nDesign a multi-platform real-time strategy game, allowing players to compete on different devices, including PCs, consoles and mobiles, with seamless synchronisation between platforms.\n\nInteractive narrative game.\nDeveloping an interactive narrative game offering an immersive experience where players'' choices directly influence the unfolding of the story, creating a unique experience for each user.\n\nOnline collaborative puzzle game.\nTo create an online puzzle game that allows several players to collaborate in real time to solve complex puzzles, encouraging cooperation and team problem-solving.'),
